# These are committed synthetic fixtures, not stray generator output. The repo
# root .gitignore excludes generated ADiGator files by name everywhere; re-include
# them here so `git add tests/fixtures/collapse` tracks them without -f.
# (The .mat is built at test runtime, not committed.)
!*_ADiGator*.m
!*_ADiGator*.mat
!*_Jac.m
